if today is [new day]
	create new daily backup
	
	if today is [start of week]
		copy oldest daily backup to weekly
	
	if today is [start of month]
		copy oldest weekly backup to monthly

	clean old backups

max_daily --> even multiple of 7 - weeks to keep as daily
max_weekly --> even multiple of 4 - months to keep as weekly
max_monthly --> any number, defualts to 1yr
